Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱拉 龙卷风的里面……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有条龙……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它移动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎 快到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫兵……没有卫兵在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着王宫去了……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
